      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, every detail confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. We invite you to experience a vehicle that defines the pinnacle of its class, offering uncompromising performance and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
