    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This FD3S stands as a superlative example of Mazda\u2019s lightweight engineering, powered by the iconic sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary engine. The powerplant exhibits excellent compression across all rotor faces, with the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbos providing a seamless transition throughout the rev range. The chassis retains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution and sophisticated four-wheel double-wishbone suspension, offering surgical turn-in and high-speed stability. Power is delivered through a crisp five-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. Meticulously maintained with no vacuum leaks or heat-cycling fatigue on the harness, this specimen features an immaculate undercarriage and original paint, representing a turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
